					AzioniPunto: "<p><b>TCM<br></b><span>•</span> Point <i>jing</i>-river and Metal of the Liver Meridian<br><span>•</span> Cleanses the stagnant Heat in the meridian<br><span>•</span> Moves Liver Qi<br><span>•</span> Regulates Lower Jiao</p><p><b>Applications</b><br><span>•</span> Swelling and retraction of the testicles<br><span>•</span> Genital pain<br><span>•</span> Urinary retention<br><span>•</span> Painful urination<br><span>•</span> Difficult urination<br><span>•</span> Seminal emission<br><span>•</span> Hypogastric pain<br><span>•</span> Shan syndromes (lower abdominal disorders)<br></p><p class=\"only_meridiani_cinesi\"><b>Needle</b><br><span>•</span> 90°, 0.3-0.5 cun<br><span>•</span> 45° medially towards 5.SP or laterally towards 41.ST<br></p><p><b>Moxibustion</b><br><span>•</span> Indicated<br></p><p><b>Location</b><br><span>•</span> On the ankle<br><span>•</span> In the deeper depression between the medial malleolus and the tendon of the tibialis anterior<br><span>•</span> Locatable with extended ankle<br></p>",
